data.title: Simcere Pharma Chairman Leads Consortium To Take Firm Private
data.meta_description: Simcere Pharmaceutical Group's majority stakeholders, which include founder- Chairman Jinsheng Ren, have offered to buy all of the China-based company considered to be worth about $500 million.
